videos.description: George Bollas delivers to Will Matthews who takes it down the sideline for a 36-yard gain, resulting in a Kent State field goal.
videos.headline: Bollas finds Matthews for big gain

videos.description: QB Nathan Rourke's 6-yard rushing touchdown puts Ohio in the lead 10-3 in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Rourke's TD puts Ohio in front

videos.description: Dorian Brown rushes 39 yards to the house for an Ohio touchdown in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Brown extends Ohio's lead

videos.description: A.J. Ouellette breaks through a tackle and runs 37 yards to the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Ouellette gets big rushing TD
